data.title: Lady Elizabeth Carteret Carteret (1663
data.meta_description: At age 13 she married her kinsman Sir Phlip Carteret (d. 1693) 2nd Baronet of St Ouen, Jersey in the Channel Islands. Her son Charles was baptised at St Margaret's Westminster on 4 June 1679 with Charles II as one of his godfathers. He was Gentleman of the Privy Chamber to Queen Anne and High Bailiff of Jersey.
